NAME
    Catalyst::Model::REST - REST model class for Catalyst

SYNOPSIS
            # model
            __PACKAGE__->config(
                    server => 'http://localhost:3000',
                    type   => 'json',
            );

            # controller
            sub foo : Local {
                    my ($self, $c) = @_;
                    my $res = $c->model('MyData')->post('foo/bar/baz', {foo => 'bar'});
                    my $code = $res->code;
                    my $data = $res->data;
                    ...
            }

DESCRIPTION
    This model class makes REST connectivety easy.

METHODS
  new
    Called from Catalyst.

  post
  get
  put
  delete
